  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This Is A Puzzle Game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You Need to Help the Cats Get into the Box.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751980/extras/17e3d35df4ccf56005c0129713bb489f.poster.avif?t=1735992083\" width=412 height=458 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751980/extras/17e3d35df4ccf56005c0129713bb489f.webm?t=1735992083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751980/extras/17e3d35df4ccf56005c0129713bb489f.mp4?t=1735992083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★200 Challenging Levels</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★casual Mode With Unlimited Fun</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★You can make your own levels to share with friends</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BGM:　Piano25 By MAOUDAMASHII</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Our latest game mode - CatEX (Cat Express)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Put the messy kittens into express boxes and pack them away</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751980/extras/e9e16ba49ec0c1ab1d4c2ec9f54a90a7.poster.avif?t=1735992083\" width=800 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751980/extras/e9e16ba49ec0c1ab1d4c2ec9f54a90a7.webm?t=1735992083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751980/extras/e9e16ba49ec0c1ab1d4c2ec9f54a90a7.mp4?t=1735992083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Free DLC-Cat Year 2022</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >a small physics game. You need to stack multiple cats of different shapes on top of each other, so that you can pass the level by keeping them from falling for a certain period of time. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751980/extras/bb62c7aa08bf15b9bcfcfd1d59759edb.poster.avif?t=1735992083\" width=412 height=458 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751980/extras/bb62c7aa08bf15b9bcfcfd1d59759edb.webm?t=1735992083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751980/extras/bb62c7aa08bf15b9bcfcfd1d59759edb.mp4?t=1735992083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★41 unstable levels </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BGM:   猫のワルツ By ゆうきわたる</strong> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The new model of the year of the ox:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move other kittens so that our \"CowCat\" can eat grass </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751980/extras/09298ed00638c38d16c8754d0b9c03fa.poster.avif?t=1735992083\" width=412 height=458 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751980/extras/09298ed00638c38d16c8754d0b9c03fa.webm?t=1735992083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751980/extras/09298ed00638c38d16c8754d0b9c03fa.mp4?t=1735992083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★30 new levels  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BGM:Kurukuru By ONTAMA</strong> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Our first DLC-Halloween mode</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three cats of different shapes are randomly generated in each round. You need to put them in the box. If the cats are connected in a line, they will become bats and fly away until the box is full. How many cats can you put in？  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751980/extras/5b708936d739ed6a426a6a31515c5f29.poster.avif?t=1735992083\" width=412 height=458 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751980/extras/5b708936d739ed6a426a6a31515c5f29.webm?t=1735992083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751980/extras/5b708936d739ed6a426a6a31515c5f29.mp4?t=1735992083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BGM:   Halloween night By Syappon</strong></p>",
